  <descriptionCdata><![CDATA[53ef3443-7975-49b1-ac02-178fe67536fb.description=<pre>\nThis operation retrieves the name of the largest file in a directory\n\nInputs\:\n\thost\:           host name to check\n\tusername\:       user name to login into host as\n\tpassword\:       password to use for login\n\tdir\:            directory to check\n\nResponses\:\n\tsuccess\:        If the file was found\n\tno such file\:   If the directory doesn't exist\n\thost not found\: If the host cannot be found\n\tauthentication failure\: If the login fails\n\tfailure\:         Any other error condition\n\nResults and Context\:\n\tThe file name is placed into the operation result\n\tThe file name is placed into the context variable "largestFile"\n\tThe size is placed into the context variable "largestFileSize"\n</pre>
]]></descriptionCdata>
